=== Overview ===
This library implements the ECSS Telemetry Transfer Frame Protocol
ECSS-E-ST-50-03C.


=== How to install ===
The TMTP library depends on the C++ library boost.

The library can be compiled with
make
sudo make install

To generate the API documentation doxygen is required and can be run with
make doc

The library will be installed under the PREFIX /usr/local


